quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  7,196,"Inna waliyyiya Allahu allatheenazzala alkitaba wahuwa yatawalla assaliheen"
  7,197,"Wallatheena tadAAoona mindoonihi la yastateeAAoona nasrakum walaanfusahum yansuroon"
  7,198,"Wa-in tadAAoohum ila alhuda layasmaAAoo watarahum yanthuroona ilayka wahumla yubsiroon"
  7,199,"Khuthi alAAafwa wa/mur bilAAurfiwaaAArid AAani aljahileen"
  7,200,"Wa-imma yanzaghannaka mina ashshaytaninazghun fastaAAith billahi innahusameeAAun AAaleem"
  7,201,"Inna allatheena ittaqaw ithamassahum ta-ifun mina ashshaytani tathakkaroofa-itha hum mubsiroon"
  7,202,"Wa-ikhwanuhum yamuddoonahum feealghayyi thumma la yuqsiroon"
  7,203,"Wa-itha lam ta/tihim bi-ayatinqaloo lawla ijtabaytaha qul innamaattabiAAu ma yooha ilayya min rabbee hathabasa-iru min rabbikum wahudan warahmatun liqawminyu/minoon"
  7,204,"Wa-itha quri-a alqur-anu fastamiAAoolahu waansitoo laAAallakum turhamoon"
  7,205,"Wathkur rabbaka fee nafsikatadarruAAan wakheefatan wadoona aljahri mina alqawli bilghuduwwiwal-asali wala takun mina alghafileen"
  7,206,"Inna allatheena AAinda rabbika layastakbiroona AAan AAibadatihi wayusabbihoonahuwalahu yasjudoon"
